thread.title: Chloe

author: Chloe
title: Chloe
text: The whole office at William Street has a great view and is very well presented. You're greeted with a smile each time you walk into reception. The Servcorp staff are extremely helpful and attentive and will go out of their way to provide any assistance needed. Offices have great space and window views of the city. Perfect size meeting rooms available if required with coffee on request! Servcorp internet is also fast with no disruptions.
